description:
Licensed physicians engaged in a practice of general or specialized
medicine and surgery that is not more accurately identified by
another more specific MCC. Such merchants include plastic and
cosmetic surgeons, dermatologists, psychiatrists, radiologists,
orthopedists, pediatricians, neurologists, obstetricians, and
gynecologists.
